---
title: Sweet Ginger Chicken with Buttery Rice & Roasted Green Beans
description: Pork chops are always a weeknight winner. They’re satisfying, speedy, and versatile, which is why our chefs are always brainstorming new ways to take ’em to the next level. The kicker this week: a fresh ginger and apricot jam pan sauce to drizzle over the chops. On the side, there’s roasted green beans and buttery jasmine rice (perfect for catching any runoff sauce).
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6422f9ce964b8ed6a409d9f1-94675d8a.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/65d64c4c55fb9bf6391b88f2.pdf
servings: 2
cuisine: Asian
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/sweet-ginger-chicken-65d64c4c55fb9bf6391b88f2
course: main course
time required: 35 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 650 kcal
  fat: 28 g
  saturated fat: 10 g
